  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: <span class=3DSpellE>Gravitic</sp=
an></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Research Preference: Speed &amp; Agility, Energy Res=
earch</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>An <span class=3DSpellE>Enton</span> is a short huma=
noid with
  pale, greyish brown skin. They appear to have large heads for their bodies
  and move in a slow purposeful manner. Other races find <span class=3DSpel=
lE>Entons</span>
  hard to empathize with in conversation because of their mostly expression=
less
  behavior.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Entons</span> are closely r=
elated
  to the <span class=3DSpellE>Kiadians</span>. The historical genetic
  relationship isn't clear and both the <span class=3DSpellE>Entons</span> =
and
  the <span class=3DSpellE>Kiadians</span> have their own ideas why their g=
enes
  are so similar.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>They are a curious race--in technology, other life a=
nd the
  history of the Galaxy. Large parts of their industry are devoted to
  philosophy, science and discovery.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>They are also very cautious, preferring to observe in
  secret. The <span class=3DSpellE>Entons</span> find other races to be very
  quick to fight, this observation has made the <span class=3DSpellE>Entons=
</span>
  grow cautious and be slightly more aggressive than they naturally are for
  their own defense.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Entons</span> have long bee=
n using
  the stealth technology of the Disbelieve Mask. Created to confuse various
  sensors the Disbelieve Mask doesn't make the <span class=3DSpellE>Enton</=
span>
  ships invisible but greatly reduces the distance their ships can be detec=
ted
  by sensors by making the ships appear like a natural occurrence or an
  anomalous signal.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Entons</span> live very solitar=
y lives
  outside of their work, many jobs for an <span class=3DSpellE>Enton</span>=
 can
  involve not seeing another <span class=3DSpellE>Enton</span> for almost t=
heir
  entire life, their only interaction being through non direct mediums of
  communication.</p>
